Changelog
=========

1.1.0
-----

 * Fixed compatibility back to Luna.
 * #4 Added flag for visibility of single lines.
 * #8 If available, new font metrics methods are being used on newer Eclipse
   versions.
 * #9 Fixed that the lines would not be visible in all editors.


1.0.1
-----

 * Changed to more accurate way of calculating the size of a character.
 * #8, Provided a way to override the measures size of a character, to work
   around a SWT bug.


1.0
---

 * Initial release.

